Text:
Rewind.
Konnie Huq presents a look back at all the highs and lows of the 2009 series of The X Factor, from the auditions - held in front of a live audience for the first time - through to the dramatic live final, in which Joe McElderry beat out Olly Murs to the title. The show features interviews with last year's finalists in which they reveal how they felt about their experiences and what life has been like for them since the series ended. Konnie also talks to the judges and previews the new series.
